text.tspan: Condom use at last high-risk sex, 2022
Share of adults of both sexes, aged 15-49 years old, who reported the use of a condom the last time they had
sexual intercourse with a non-marital, non-cohabiting sexual partner in the past 12 months.
Data source: Joint United Nations Programme on HIV/AIDS (2024)
